text:
Anna Cathcart (born June 16, 2003) is a Canadian child actress. She played Olympia in "Odd Squad", Dizzy in the Disney Channel original movies "Descendants 2" and "3", Kitty in the Netflix original movie "To All the Boys I've Loved Before" and Zoe in Zoe Valentine.
Early life.
Cathcart was born in Richmond, Canada on June 16, 2003, and raised in Vancouver, Canada. She has an older sister called Sara Cathcart. Cathcart currently goes to school.
